node.text: charcoal choux pastry from @matchayasg delivered by my friend 🤩🤩 tbh when they first came i didnt know what they were, but once i took a bite this rich creamy but surprisingly light filling just engulfed ma mouth. the charcoal lowkey tasted like oreos but less sweet. the matcha and hojicha taste was reaaally rich which i liked but the winner for me was black sesame 🤩🤩🤩 it was so good i forgot to stop and take a pic. the filling was sweeter than the other 2 and paired really nicely with the pseudo-oreo crust 🥺🥺🥺
The matcha one is my all-time fav!!😍
I do that too!! 😂 especially when something looks as good as this 🤤
The consistency of the cream is on point! 🙌🏻😍
Thanks for sharing @matchayasg! We will like to extend you a $10 off via “LIKEMATCHAYA$10” on //matchaya.sg
